{"tid":757707,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"駐校已婚56歲社工 翟光輝 涉強姦非禮中五女生   還柙候訊","createTime":"2018-07-27T05:26:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T06:15:31.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fed4bd56a929817cd7c9a0bc95b4bb3846f701fa","tid":757707,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T05:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180727/large/1532668098_74b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180727%2Flarge%2F1532668098_74b1.jpg&h=318780e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180727/58492481\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180727%2F58492481&d=5SQu4Df4Zm6QU7pBGlGX%2BEzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=c605c4fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180727%2F58492481&h=125bf228\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180727/58492481</a><br />\n<br />\n特殊學校駐校已婚社工，涉嫌非禮甚至強姦輕度智障的17歲中五女生。直至女生親友在女生手機內發現她與社工間的可疑WhatsApp訊息，查問下揭發本案。警方接報拘捕涉案社工，落案控以一項強姦及五項非禮罪，案件今在沙田裁判法院提堂，並押後待警方繼續調查，被告不准保釋，還柙至下月24日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n被告社工翟光輝（56歲）報住在元朗錦綉花園。他被指於去年12月17至今年6月9日間，分別在校內、西餐廳、荃灣公園及公屋停車場內非禮女童X，其中在校內非禮兩次。他另被控於今年4月4日在一個天台單位強姦X。<br />\n<br />\n被告暫時毋須答辯。控方申請押後，讓警方繼續調查案件，並指因控罪性質嚴重，擔心被告會干擾證人，反對被告保釋。辯方為被告提出保釋申請，但裁判官最終拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：STCC2891/18】"},{"pid":"008decce0e8341a21106948b3e71fd2d682e2e22","tid":757707,"uid":73722,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T05:28:01.000Z","msg":"要求加返宮刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eda99fcfdd973b9e024a6ed1dafea26d3387e1b","tid":757707,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"008decce0e8341a21106948b3e71fd2d682e2e22","tid":757707,"uid":73722,"like":1,"d